{
  "stem": "16059.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was advanced, but not knowing the language very well, it was difficult to relate to the teachers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I knew what they were doing but couldn't speak properly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, we moved to Indianapolis, so another culture shock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because that was different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was small town-- small town and a lot of anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So here I was again, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Got it again.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Had to kind of keep quiet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Don't tell anybody you're Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Don't mention it in school, because, you know, you don't want them to know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My parents had difficulty getting jobs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They don't speak English.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were refugees, and they were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we moved to a basement apartment, which was like a prison.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was no bedroom.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was one big kitchen with a drain in the middle for the washing machine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But it was made into an apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And first of all, before that, we moved into a house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "A, a lady owned this house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She was a widow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was rat-infested.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had one room for the four of us, my sister, Vivienne, and Mom and Dad.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was just rat-infested.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "All night long, I would hear the rats and the mice going at each other.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was just-- it was horrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And to this day, I cannot stand those animals because of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But this lady did not clean her home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it was just-- it was a devastating situation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we finally-- we moved somewhere else, which was not much better and then ended up in this basement apartment.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And like I said, it was a big kitchen-- kitchen, I don't know-- cabinets, a basement, and one other room.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I slept in a hallway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were stairs next to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
